trans_title: 百变水族箱 第一季
introduction: "You can dream it, We can build it."Brothers-in-law by marriage. Business partners by choice. Wayde King and Brett Raymer know how to joke around. But they also know how to create some of the most amazing aquariums around. Along with the rest of Acrylic Tank Manufacturing (ATM), featured in Animal Planet's new series Tanked, they deliver the laughs while doing business with some big names. Tune in Fridays at 9 PM E/P, beginning August 19.
